headline: Gas vs. Coal: The Impact of Volatile Natural Gas Prices on Power
summary: Energy By Trevor Fugita | April 17, 2025 The energy world of the early 2010s looked starkly different from today. U.S. LNG exports were in their infancy, with Sabine Pass yet to commence operations....
